  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help 100 Thai children get an education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For many families in Northern Thailand, education is a luxury they cannot afford. Education Matters, our scholarship program, supports low income families to send their children to school by covering educational costs including tuition, school lunch and uniforms. By supporting children to complete high school and even attend university, these children will grow up better equipped to provide for their families, thus ending the vicious cycle of poverty, abuse and neglect.</narrative>
  </description>
